{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"call_f31DxFrOwQuGAlw5949NWK01","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t---\n2\tinput:\n3\t  request: string\n4\t---\n5\t\n6\tBuild a complete, working application inside the current project from a natural-language\n7\t`request`, ONE FILE AT A TIME. The pipeline first DESIGNS the app (an appId, tables, endpoints,\n8\tpages, hooks), then creates the project and writes each file with the injected authoring globals\n9\t(`createProject`/`writeTableSchema`/`writeApi`/`writePage`/`writeHook`) — the host runs the steps\n10\tin dependency order and fans the per-table / per-endpoint / per-page / per-hook steps out for you,\n11\teach writing exactly one file. Every table/column/relation carries a real description; pages use\n12\t`@lmthing/css` design tokens only.\n13\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"call_XOUkCCKPWXZ8vWn7RxhEWgPz","session_id":"625ee3e5-57b1-42a3-9cc2-762259deb6f8","uuid":"88c8375b-c222-400c-baf1-538f62b15096","timestamp":"2026-07-16T03:55:45.351Z","subagent_type":"Explore","task_description":"Trace automator build failure"}
